# Global Variable Lists (GVLs)

This directory contains global variable lists that are accessible throughout the project.

## Naming Conventions

- Global Variable Lists: `GVL_` prefix (e.g., `GVL_Config`, `GVL_Constants`)

## Best Practices

- Keep GVLs organized by purpose (parameters, constants, status)
- Avoid overuse of global variables
- Use CONSTANT or PERSISTENT attributes where appropriate
- Document the purpose of each GVL
- Consider using parameter lists for configuration data
